name: Bi-Metal Hole Saw Kit, 9 Pieces Drill Hole Saw Set in Case with Mandrels, Hole Saw Bits, Hex Wrench Key for General Purpose Applications in Metal, Hard Wood, Plastic Plate, PVS Board, Steel
short_description: ✅ What You Get: Hole saw set includes a compact storage case with 6PCS saw blades - 3/4" (19mm), 7/8" (22mm), 1-1/8" (29mm), 1-1/2" (38mm), 1-3/4" (44mm), 2" (51mm), 1 X 7/16" hex mandrel, 1 X 1/4"mandrel, 2 X drill bits, 1 X hex key.

✅ High Quality: M42 Bi-Metal drill hole saw kit crafted from premium quality M42 steel with 8% cobalt ensures exceptional toughness and extended lifespan. The rock-solid wood hole saw kit blades have a wide slot on each hole saw to effectively remove sawdust, swarf and plugs.

✅ Application: The AV Steel bi-metal hole saw kit is a reliable and durable tool set suitable for making holes in a wide range of materials including metal, hard wood, PVC board, plastic, cork boards, drywall, and plasterboard.

✅ Tip #1: Metal needs to be drilled at low speeds; the larger the diameter, the lower the speed. It is also recommended to drill steel with coolant to prevent high tooth tip temperatures from cracking the cutting edge.

✅ Tip #2: By applying a light coating of anti-corrosion oil to the filter surface, you can prevent natural oxidation and prolong the hole saw lifespan. Do not exceed a cutting depth of approximately 1-1/2" (38mm) with this tool.
✅ Tip #3: 7/16" hex arbor is applied to 1-1/2" (38mm), 1-3/4" (44mm), 2" (51mm) hole saw blades and 1/4" mandrel is applied to 3/4" (19mm), 7/8" (22mm), 1-1/8" (29mm) hole saw blades.
✅ Tip #4: This product is not applicable for making holes in a concrete floor, glass, and ceramic tile.

Twice as durable as our previous generation when cutting through metal, these bi-metal hole saws feature thicker walls to minimize tooth loss and improve durability. short_description: ALL-IN-ONE KIT: Features two spinlock universal arbors, steel pilot bit and six hole saws with progressor tooth design
SPINLOCK UNIVERSAL ARBOR: Fits all brands and sizes to simplify diameter changes with fast plug removal and tool-free install
THE PILOT BIT: Designed to start holes in a variety of materials
PROGRESSOR TOOTH DESIGN: Hole saws feature alternating teeth size for performance, cutting faster and lasting longer in wood, metal and plastic materials
DURABLE HOLE SAW MATERIAL: Hole saws are made with 8% cobalt alloy
REINFORCED SHOULDERS: Provide added strength and longer life to the hole saws
PLASTIC CASE: Organizes and protects kit
product_description: The Bosch 9 pc. General Purpose Bi-Metal Hole Saw Kit is designed for users who are looking for convenient way to get clean fast cuts in such materials as wood, aluminum, metal and plastic. The kit comes with six hole saw sizes: 3/4 In., 7/8 In., 1-1/8 In., 1-1/2 In., 1-3/4 In. and 2 In. The universal arbor fits all brands and sizes to simplify diameter changes, facilitates faster plug removal and enables tool-free accessory install. It’s made to let you change hole saws in seconds. The pilot bit is designed for a variety of materials as well. The hole saws feature the Progressor tooth design, which features alternating teeth size for performance, cutting faster and lasting longer in wood, aluminum, metal and plastic materials. The 2-in-1 cuts are clean and fast. Large teeth are optimized for fast cuts in thick materials; small teeth are optimized for clean cuts in thin material. The hole saws are made with 8% cobalt alloy and are designed with reinforced shoulders.
